{"tha-ap554:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap554:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap554:0.3":"Nadikassapattheraapadana ","tha-ap554:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap554:1.2":"Lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap554:1.3":"Pindacaram carantassa, ","tha-ap554:1.4":"Varato uttamam yasam; ","tha-ap554:1.5":"Aggaphalam gahetvana, ","tha-ap554:1.6":"Adasim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap554:2.1":"Tena kammena devindo, ","tha-ap554:2.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap554:2.3":"Sampattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap554:2.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap554:3.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap554:3.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap554:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap554:3.4":"aggadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap554:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap554:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap554:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap554:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap554:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap554:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap554:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap554:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap554:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap554:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nadikassapo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap554:8.1":"Nadikassapattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}